n Drugs hint at the wide circulation and availability of written medical knowledge at the beginning of the fourth century BCE.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 4aAntike Medizin. 4aCorpus Hippocraticum. 4aGriechische Medizin.  aAncient Medicine.  aCorpus Hippocraticum.  aGreek Medicine.1 aPérez Cañizares, Pilar, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2024 Part 1z978311133219208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2023 Englishz978311131908708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2023z9783111318110oZDB-23-DGD0 cprintz978311100029940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311102659640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111026596423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111026596/original  a978-3-11-131908-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-133219-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2024 Part 1b2024  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_MDPM  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  aEBA_ECL_MDPM  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGDb2023  aZDB-23-DGGb2023